{"tid":585712,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"屌你根本唔係唱功既問題","createTime":"2018-03-09T02:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T11:20:46.000Z","uid":64136,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"abf2053a761ab0afeba74b315185c777dd597341","tid":585712,"uid":64136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:02:53.000Z","msg":"呢幾年係咁標榜<br />\n高音要有咁高得咁高<br />\n震音要有咁震得咁震<br />\n條氣要有咁長得咁長<br />\n<br />\n俾啲低質支那節目拉抵哂聽歌既標準<br />\n<br />\n唱功根本唔係重點，重點係你有無心去唱<br />\n份詞有無心作，曲有無心編<br />\n有無擺靈魂落去<br />\n<br />\n聽返 beyond - 無悔這一生<br />\n一段黃貫中 之後到一段黃家駒<br />\n比起上黎黃家駒把聲又牛又蒼<br />\n<br />\n但一樣唱入心<br />\n<br />\n能衝一次 多一次 不息自強<br />\n<br />\n唔好再尻嗌啦，傷耳呀！"},{"pid":"aebd06f1e37b62838f3ccef11ba69ed80d3111bf","tid":585712,"uid":27210,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"全部廢話，但例子用beyond 即刻俾正評"},{"pid":"beab9de13fcd61920c435b159c9085ff3a3b448f","tid":585712,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aaade154581e66028f790581fb7de8bf4378632","tid":585712,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0be9070ae35eb80b0fdbd0ea7b2892d0488d805a","tid":585712,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f684963900b4b38791618ba7a96ea34d44c72e4","tid":585712,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beab9de13fcd61920c435b159c9085ff3a3b448f","tid":585712,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:09:49.000Z","msg":"小蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca463e9fc2c5103a14c6bffa738c767f8fce235","tid":585712,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5a35